<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Adoption Request Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #555;
        }

        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a {
            color: #008080;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Update on Your Adoption Request</h1>

        <p>Hello <%= adopterName %>,</p>

        <p>This email is regarding your adoption request for <strong>
                <%= petName %>
            </strong>.</p>

        <p>Unfortunately, the lister has decided not to proceed with your request at this time. We understand this may
            be disappointing news.</p>

        <p>There are many other wonderful pets waiting for homes on PawPal. We encourage you to continue browsing:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
            <!-- You'll need to pass the full URL to the browse page -->
            <a href="<%= browsePetsUrl %>"
                style="background-color: #008080; color: white; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none;">Browse
                Available Pets</a>
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for considering adoption through PawPal.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            The PawPal Team
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>